Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.65,Caption,,0,0,0,,Flight 501 was its very first launch.\NThe maiden voyage.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.65,0:00:09.30,Caption,,0,0,0,,On board sat four scientific satellites\Ncalled Cluster — a
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.30,0:00:13.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,mission years in the making, built to\Nstudy the Earth's
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.35,Caption,,0,0,0,,magnetic field. Irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.69,0:00:19.32,Caption,,0,0,0,,Now — a rocket is only as smart as the
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,computer flying it. And that computer\Nneeds to know one
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,thing above all else: which way is up.\NHow is
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.21,Caption,,0,0,0,,it tilted, how fast is it turning, where\Nis it
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.48,Caption,,0,0,0,,pointed. That job belongs to a component\Ncalled the
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.48,0:00:34.57,Caption,,0,0,0,,Inertial Reference System.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.59,Caption,,0,0,0,,Ariane 5 carried two of them — a main\Nunit
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.59,0:00:41.90,Caption,,0,0,0,,and a backup — constantly measuring the\Nrocket's motion
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.90,0:00:45.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,and feeding it to the flight computer,\Nso the engines
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.58,0:00:46.32,Caption,,0,0,0,,could steer.
